#summary links to technical documentation for the SkyTraq Venus child found online

At the time of writing this I found several documents with the specification online: 
  * [http://www.mr-lee-catcam.de/BINARY/skytraq_AN0003_v3_binary_message.pdf Application Note AN0003 - Binary Messages Of SkyTraq Venus 5 GPS Receiver] - this describes how to configure the GPS receiver itself
  * [http://www.nabble.com/attachment/17855164/1/AN0008_v048_%20datalog%20extesion.pdf Application Note AN0008 - Data Logging Extension For Venus 5 GPS Receiver] - configuration and download of tracks from the data logger
